io.earcam.unexceptional

Interface EmeticStream<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the element type of this stream
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface EmeticStream<T>

    EmeticStream provides a functional parallel to Stream, with methods taking checked equivalents of java.util.function

    emetic

    /ɪˈmɛtɪk/ 

    adjective:

    1. (of a substance) causing vomiting.
